text: Toujiacuo () is a railway station on the TRA Taichung line located in Tanzi District, Taichung, Taiwan. It opened on 28 October 2018. ==See also== * List of railway stations in Taiwan ==References== ==External links== Category:2018 establishments in Taiwan Category:Railway stations in Taichung Category:Railway stations opened in 2018 Category:Railway stations served by Taiwan Railways Administration
